                    <h4 style="border-bottom:2px solid #e67e22; color:#333;">5. Medical & Allergies</h4>
                    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:5px; margin-bottom:15px; font-size:0.75rem;">
